title: 1 Month FREE! Wood-Plank Floors, Modern Finishes, Impressive Amenities
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Toni Hill | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '1BR/Alcove/1BA Apartment - Minneapolis', 'W Lake St, Minneapolis, MN 55408', '$1360/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '650 sqft.', 'Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Parking:', 'Garage Parking is $100/Mo', 'Lease Duration:', '8-14 Months', 'Deposit:', '$300', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Your first-class ticket to everything Uptown!', 'Ideally located, our stylish community of studio, one, two, and three-bedroom apartments put you in the epicenter of all the action.', 'Quick access to buzzy restaurants, hip bars, eclectic boutiques, and refreshing nature trails, combined with the thoughtful on-site amenities, make our Uptown Minneapolis apartments the place to be.', 'Our perfect walk score means you will only have to take a couple of steps to find some cool ways to spend your afternoon.', 'From attending the signature Uptown Art Fair to having a relaxed weekend in nature at the iconic Chain of Lakes or catching an indie movie at the landmark Uptown Theater, you will never run out of things to do.', 'Our spacious apartments offer a private patio, high ceilings, upgraded appliances, and designer interiors - everything you need to feel right at home.', 'A business center, seasonal hot tub, intimate fitness studio, and quaint courtyard with BBQ area, coupled with attached garage parking, night patrol, and package receiving services complete your all-play, zero-stress experience.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', '•Granite Coutertops', '•High Speed Internet Access', '• In-Unit Washer/Dryer', '•Air Conditioning', '•Smoke Free', '•Cable Ready', '•Storage Units', '•Fireplace*', '•Pantry', '•Island Kitchen', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', '•"Smart" building technology', '•24-hour emergency maintenance', '•Advanced heating and cooling system', '•BBQ/Picnic Area', '•Condominium-style finishes', '•Contemporary urban-styles kitchens', '•Flat panel cherry wood kitchen cabinets', '•High Ceilings', '•Large walk-in closets with organizers', '•Oversized 36" roman soaking tubs', '•Panoramic views', '•Private plaza with outdoor fireplace and hot tubs', '•Storage Space', '•Underground heated parking', 'Contact info:', 'Toni Hill', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
